    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one and it literally looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! No scratches, no smells, just pure perfection. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for, this is the one. Come see it for yourself, you won't be disappointed!",
