    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Available is a museum-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of the S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This engine retains its factory-spec compression and exhibits zero VANOS rattle, with rod bearings proactively replaced to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly integrity. The chassis is structurally optimized with a reinforced rear subframe, mitigating the common fatigue points of the platform. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-Differential, providing exceptional lockup and traction. The suspension geometry is preserved with fresh bushings and original dampers, maintaining the communicative hydraulic steering feel. This is a turnkey, analog masterpiece for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
