    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage, shielded from the elements and road debris. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is a pristine time capsule; the premium leather seats show no signs of creasing or bolster wear, and the original factory scent remains. Every button, switch, and electronic feature operates with crisp, tactile precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule using only genuine OEM parts. There are no leaks, no rattles, and the engine bay is detailed to show-quality standards. This is a rare opportunity for a collector to own an example that defies its age. Sold complete with all original keys, manuals, and a comprehensive service history binder.",
